  "2026-04-01T13:06:48.719Z",codex-agent,Task exists to enforce compatibility and prevent regressions from default-behavior changes.
  "2026-04-01T13:24:24.814Z",codex-agent,"Added regression coverage for semantic defaults and compatibility guardrails in tests/unit/semantic-defaults.spec.ts, tests/unit/search-command.spec.ts, and tests/helpers/withTempPmPath.ts (deterministic integration harness control). Evidence: pm test pm-9k33 --run passed all linked suites including full node scripts/run-tests.mjs test (62 files, 648 tests). Coverage command executed and failed only on existing global 100% threshold policy (97.92 lines, 96.05 branches, 98.41 functions, 97.74 statements)."
